ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: This course really is a deep dive into the topic of Systems Biology, using a great selection of papers and training critical thinking skills. Would definitely recommend.
I highly recommend the course. It did help a lot familiarizing the concepts, approaches, and research topics in system biology. And I like the class format.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: It really helped thinking about research in a new way and prompted students to think about research topics that could still be addressed. Very useful especially for Grad students when it comes to designing their own research.
